POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "帮我分析最近一周的科技新闻趋势",
  "context": "关注 AI 领域"
}

### 定义变量
@task_id=628ff96e-cfb7-416d-922c-ee9ab72a52b4

### 执行任务
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/{{task_id}}/execute
Content-Type: application/json

### 查询任务状态
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks/{{task_id}}